data.description: Good size brick veneer home in San Juan. Typical floor plan with 1 living and 2 dining areas. . A beautiful 4/ 2/2 house located in a nice, quite neighborhood. Large size bedrooms with spacious closets. Large, spacious kitchen with dinning area & breakfast nook with custom cabinets, granite counter top & two skylights. Backyard has a covered patio and a covered area with cemented flooring & surrounded with private wooden fence. Front yard has new grass/ garden with sprinkler system. Water softening system available if buyer is interested In keeping.
